45
00:03:42,302 --> 00:03:47,164
[SPEAKER_06]: It's currently a 200 unit 11 story high rise building.

46
00:03:47,885 --> 00:03:53,107
[SPEAKER_06]: We are looking to do a perform a complete gut modernization of the building.

47
00:03:54,302 --> 00:04:01,824
[SPEAKER_06]: The building's currently laid out as 181-bedroom units and 22-bedroom units.

48
00:04:02,784 --> 00:04:11,726
