50
00:04:21,043 --> 00:04:24,246
[SPEAKER_06]: This all-install building was built between 1963 and 1965.

51
00:04:24,386 --> 00:04:29,610
[SPEAKER_06]: It has not been comprehensively modernized since then.

52
00:04:30,571 --> 00:04:34,734
[SPEAKER_06]: The electrical is all original.

53
