55
00:04:40,539 --> 00:04:43,201
[SPEAKER_06]: And as I stated, this gut modernization will

56
00:04:45,113 --> 00:04:47,653
[SPEAKER_06]: be replacing all the plumbing, all the electrical.

57
00:04:47,834 --> 00:04:51,654
[SPEAKER_06]: We'll be bringing central air conditioning and heating to the building.

58
00:04:52,594 --> 00:04:55,055
